mil.nga.giat.geowave.analytics.tools

Class PropertyManagement

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.analytics.tools.PropertyManagement

  • public class PropertyManagement
extends Object
    Manage properties used by the Map Reduce environment that are provided through the API (e.g. command). Allow these arguments to be placed an 'args' list for 'main' executables (e.g. ToolRunner).
